dcterms:description: A synthetic dataset built by composing sub-sessions from the available data on Shop X, containing 1,075,000 sessions, with 375,000 sessions that include search interactions reflecting known proportions of relevant and irrelevant interactions.
dcterms:title: Synthetic Dataset (SD)

dcterms:description: An industry dataset obtained by collecting anonymized sessions from June 2019 to September 2019 from a partnering Shop X, containing 912,884 sessions used for prod2vec training and 10,000 sampled converting sessions with search.
dcterms:title: Industry Dataset (ID)
